Type: Package
Package: RGISTools
Title: Tools for handling multiplatform satellite images.
Version: 0.9.5
Author: U PÃ©rez - Goya [aut, cre] <unai.perez@unavarra.es>,
        A F Militino [aut] <militino@unavarra.es>,
